OL,3,CEx-police officer admits trying to
OL,4,Ckill former partner by ramming car
OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FA former policeman has been convicted
OL,8,Fof attempting to murder his ex-partner
OL,9,Fand her mother by driving his car
OL,10,Fthrough the window of their funeral
OL,11,Fdirector's shop.
OL,13,FWilliam McBurnie scarred Zoe Turnbull
OL,14,Ffor life and caused serious harm to
OL,15,Fher 71-year-old mother Beverley in the
OL,16,Fincident in the Scottish Borders town
OL,17,Fof Jedburgh in December 2022.
