OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FAt the High Court in Livingston on
OL,8,FMonday Judge Lord Mulholland described
OL,9,Fthe accused's deliberate bid to kill
OL,10,Fhis former partner as a "cowardly and
OL,11,Fselfish act".
OL,13,FHe told the 67-year-old to be under no
OL,14,Fillusion that he was going to be sent
OL,15,Fto prison for "a very long time".
