OL,3,CEx-police officer admits trying to
OL,4,Ckill former partner by ramming car
OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FThe court heard that McBurnie, a
OL,8,Fformer advanced driver and driving
OL,9,Finstructor with the Police Service of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, had been drinking
OL,11,Fwhisky since 6am on the day of the
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FHe was nearly three times the drink
OL,15,Fdrive limit when he deliberately
OL,16,Faccelerated along an adjoining street
OL,17,Fand drove "at speed" through a give
OL,18,Fway sign towards the shop in Market
OL,19,FStreet.
