OL,3,CEx-police officer admits trying to
OL,4,Ckill former partner by ramming car
OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FHis car mounted the pavement, smashed
OL,8,Fthrough two large flower planters and
OL,9,Fthrough the plate glass window,
OL,10,Fsending glass flying everywhere and
OL,11,Fhitting the office desk so hard it was
OL,12,Fimpaled in a rear wall.
OL,14,FCCTV footage of the incident shows how
OL,15,Fclose McBurnie came to hitting both
OL,16,Fwomen as they pressed themselves
OL,17,Fagainst the side walls of the office.
OL,19,FAs he climbed out of the wreckage the
OL,20,Ftwo women were seen in the background
OL,21,Fhugging each other outside the shop.
