OL,3,CEx-police officer admits trying to
OL,4,Ckill former partner by ramming car
OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FAdvocate depute Alex Price Marmion
OL,8,Fsaid McBurnie had been seen stopping
OL,9,Fhis car at the junction opposite the
OL,10,Fshop on two occasions the previous
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FOn the day of the attack he was again
OL,14,Fseen pausing at the junction before
OL,15,Fturning to the right and driving off
OL,16,Fafter a customer left the undertakers.
