OL,7,FMoments later, after driving round a
OL,8,Ftriangle of roads in Jedburgh town
OL,9,Fcentre, Miss Turnbull spotted
OL,10,FMcBurnie's car speeding straight
OL,11,Ftowards the glass-fronted office.
OL,13,FShe shouted to her mother, who was
OL,14,Fstanding behind a frosted glass panel
OL,15,Fof the front window: "He's coming!
OL,16,FHe's coming! He's coming through the
OL,17,Fwindow!"
