OL,7,FShe pinned herself against the side
OL,8,Fwall of the office as the accused's
OL,9,Fcar crashed through, narrowly missing
OL,10,Fthe two of them.
OL,12,FThe accused, who suffered a burn
OL,13,Finjury to his wrist as the car's
OL,14,Fairbags went off, immediately said:
OL,15,F"Sorry. I don't know what I was
OL,16,Fthinking."
