OL,7,FThe advocate depute said Miss
OL,8,FTurnbull, 46, had suffered a bruised
OL,9,Fleg and had since been diagnosed with
OL,10,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder as a
OL,11,Fresult of the incident.
OL,13,FShe also now had tinnitus, deafness in
OL,14,Fher right ear and a low tolerance of
OL,15,Fnoise and had experienced two episodes
OL,16,Fof cardiac arrest from "broken heart
OL,17,Fsyndrome", caused by extreme stress.
