OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FHer mother had experienced atrial
OL,8,Ffibrillation, breathlessness and
OL,9,Ffatigue. Both women submitted victim
OL,10,Fimpact statements to the court.
OL,12,FThe advocate depute said the accused
OL,13,Fhad been drinking heavily for several
OL,14,Fmonths following the break-up of his
OL,15,Frelationship with Miss Turnbull and
OL,16,Fhad been behaving in an increasingly
OL,17,Falarming manner towards her.
