OL,3,CEx-police officer admits trying to
OL,4,Ckill former partner by ramming car
OL,5,Cinto shop
OL,7,FHe had bombarded her with unwanted
OL,8,Ftexts, phone calls and emails and
OL,9,Frepeatedly turned up at her office
OL,10,Fbegging her to restart their
OL,11,Frelationship.
OL,13,FGareth Jones, defending, said
OL,14,FMcBurnie, had expressed "genuine
OL,15,Fremorse" for his actions.
OL,17,FHe added that the accused only had a
OL,18,Fvague recollection of what was going
OL,19,Fthrough his mind about Zoe Turnbull at
OL,20,Fthe time of the offence.
