OL,7,FHowever, he accepted that his actions
OL,8,Fhad been "entirely reckless" and that
OL,9,Fhe had done it with the intention of
OL,10,Fkilling her.
OL,12,FThe court called for background
OL,13,Freports and adjourned the case until
OL,14,FThursday 19 September at Livingston.
OL,15,FMcBurnie was remanded in custody until
OL,16,Fthen.
